dcterms:description: The MSCOCO dataset contains free form texts which are human annotations of images. It is noted for having paraphrase pairs that contain more novel words and syntactic manipulations compared to other datasets.
dcterms:title: MSCOCO

dcterms:description: The QUORA dataset contains over 120k examples of question pairs used for paraphrase generation. It is utilized to evaluate the performance of paraphrase generation models.
dcterms:title: QUORA
